flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Receive coding<br/>problem description"]
    B --> C[Generate test cases]
    C --> D[Implement Python solution]
    D --> E[Execute all tests in parallel]
    E --> F{All tests pass?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Return verified function]
    G --> H([End])
    F -->|No| I{Max iterations<br/>reached?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Return best attempt<br/>with failure report]
    J --> H
    I -->|No| K[Analyze test failures]
    K --> L{Revise tests,<br/>code, or both?}
    L -->|Revise tests| C
    L -->|Revise code| D
    L -->|Revise both| C